"{\"uid\": \"kval.com-news-local-carey-excited-for-second-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Now  52\\u00b0  Sat  51\\u00b0  Sun  52\\u00b0  byRonald Clark  EUGENE, Ore -It's just days away from the opening ceremony of the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris, and one of the main events expected to garner attention is women's gymnastics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 136, \"end\": 141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999988964810149, \"rank\": 1.1035202158923057e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the last couple of years, the sport has become a main spectacle on the docket of events and this year's USA roster is expected to compete for gold once again.\", \"from\": 223, \"to\": 386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 332, \"end\": 335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.8872038168118033, \"rank\": 0.11391204259868022, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The squad includes one new comer in Hezly Rivera, but returns four stars from the previous team: Suni Lee, Jordan Chiles, Simone Biles, and Oregon state's own Jade Carey.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 430, \"end\": 436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.9958558210268924, \"rank\": 0.0033661914645998093, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\"}, {\"begin\": 485, \"end\": 493, \"title\": \"http://dbped